    },
    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn19.10:1.1",
          "pli": "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ kumbhaṇḍaṃ purisaṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantaṃ. ",
          "en": "“Just now, reverend, as I was descending from Vulture’s Peak Mountain I saw a man with testicles as big as pots flying through the air. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.10:1.2",
          "pli": "So gacchantopi teva aṇḍe khandhe āropetvā gacchati. ",
          "en": "When he was walking he had to lift his testicles on to his shoulder. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.10:1.3",
          "pli": "Nisīdantopi tesveva aṇḍesu nisīdati. ",
          "en": "And when he sat down, he sat right on them. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.10:1.4",
          "pli": "Tamenaṃ gijjhāpi kākāpi kulalāpi anupatitvā anupatitvā vitacchenti virājenti. ",
          "en": "Vultures, crows, and hawks kept chasing him, pecking, plucking, and hacking "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.10:1.5",
          "pli": "So sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe … ",
          "en": "as he screamed in pain. …” … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.10:1.6",
          "pli": "eso, bhikkhave, satto imasmiṃyeva rājagahe gāmakūṭako ahosi … pe …. ",
          "en": "“That being used to be a corrupt official right here in Rājagaha. …” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.10:1.7",
          "pli": "Dasamaṃ. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.10:1.8",
          "pli": "Paṭhamo vaggo. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.10:2.1",
          "pli": "Aṭṭhi pesi ubho gāvaghātakā, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.10:2.2",
          "pli": "Piṇḍo sākuṇiyo nicchavorabbhi; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.10:2.3",
          "pli": "Asi sūkariko sattimāgavi, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.10:2.4",
          "pli": "Usu kāraṇiko sūci sārathi; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.10:2.5",
          "pli": "Yo ca sibbiyati sūcako hi so, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.10:2.6",
          "pli": "Aṇḍabhāri ahu gāmakūṭakoti. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
